  "detailed_description": "A top-down wizard brawler about spell drafting and beard envy, MageQuit allows 10 mages to battle it out online or locally. Beards grow longer with each kill; the wizard with the longest beard after 9 rounds wins!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2-10 players (online or local)<br></li><li>Anonymous matchmaking<br></li><li>Spell drafting<br></li><li>Spell curving<br></li><li>Full controller support<br></li><li>Mouse and keyboard support<br>(more info: <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/572220/discussions/0/1814296907960847790/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >https://steamcommunity.com/app/572220/discussions/0/1814296907960847790/</a>)<br></li><li>35 different spells (35 more coming)<br></li><li>Teams or free for all<br></li><li>Dynamic original sound track</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WAYS TO PLAY MAGEQUIT</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Playing solo?</strong> Choose anonymous matchmaking.<br></li><li><strong>Have 1 or 2 friends over?</strong> Connect more controllers and choose anonymous matchmaking.<br></li><li><strong>Have a group of 4 to 10 at your house?</strong> Play locally.<br></li><li><strong>Have 1 or 2 friends online?</strong> Party up and choose anonymous matchmaking.<br></li><li><strong>Have a group of 4 to 10 online?</strong> Play online, party only.</li></ul>",
